text: and there is one other thing I know it's
not for Europe but there is another
Christmas tradition from another part of
the world that you really should know
about and that is eating KFC fried
chicken and Christmas is a Japanese
tradition even place that aren't KFC
they have actually chicken orders out
there so you might need to order it a
month in advance to make sure you eat
your fried chicken for Christmas here in
Japan so just an FYI on that one
